{"tid":2388471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街訪英國人：港中產移民可帶動英國經濟 但憂武肺脫歐夾撃下適應艱難","createTime":"2021-01-31T07:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T18:48:04.000Z","uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9098cf7a98f9d74009ee28caf7a193a09dad6c","tid":2388471,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"BNO居英簽證正式開放申請，英國內政部料近300萬合資格港人中，有14萬或會在今年申請簽證。但受武肺及脫歐雙重夾撃，當地失業率最新攀升至5％，料年中有260萬人失業，當地人到底如何看待這班港人移民新力軍？《蘋果》特約記者在倫敦訪問當地人看法，大部分對政策表示。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n30多歲的Ben認為，英國身為香港前宗主國，有道義為港人提供入籍途徑。他明白此舉會增加當地人就業壓力及推高樓價，現時亦未是最好時機接收港人，但他認為英國政府執政方針都是有利中產。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n27歲法國籍Carolyn在2012年移居英國，已取得當地永久居留權。她認為許多本地人都失業，包括自己原本是餐廳經理，但因疫情失去工作，要冒險到武肺檢測中心當清潔工。她指當本地人也一職難求，擔心大批前來的港人會令職場競爭更大。不過她同時指脫歐令大批原本在英國生活的移民工回流歐盟國家，故港人。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於在英國生活已22年的哥倫比亞裔Andy認為，BNO簽證是個很好的措施，可提供誘因讓港人創業，甚至創造更多職位給當地人。他認為所有行業都需要人才，只要大家都對社會有貢獻，他不會視港人移民措施擾人，反而視為發展良機。<br />\n<br />\n有不少英人歡迎港人，但亦有人擔心會加劇貧富懸殊。不願上鏡的42歲英國人Elaine表示，以現時倫敦西北面為例，樓價已比15年前推高45％，如大批港人來英國買樓，會令本地人更難上車，同時增加了就業市場競爭，或會令更多人流浪街頭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210131/JGM7SUDFC5E4RKZLUCZ6WHNH6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210131%2FJGM7SUDFC5E4RKZLUCZ6WHNH6U%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=002def73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210131%2FJGM7SUDFC5E4RKZLUCZ6WHNH6U%2F&h=dd9b3739\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210131/JGM7SUDFC5E4RKZLUCZ6WHNH6U/</a>"},{"pid":"68a4d17f79c94626ba67983723a1d60616d0014d","tid":2388471,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoYTmAq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoYTmAq.jpg&h=efe22e31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f5d9e17077d95de295a14cb171f354232dbff58","tid":2388471,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"上鏡班人未必真係講真心說話"},{"pid":"ec8574e47710f08c1ec002d5943b4a8387ccf2db","tid":2388471,"uid":342990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"carolyn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2e28576ccb9df4650fb60ffbce3d6232b6b8be","tid":2388471,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T18:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fda380b77ae55b1c2c19b9cf76b6b6e11a03ee","tid":2388471,"uid":384590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f5d9e17077d95de295a14cb171f354232dbff58","tid":2388471,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"上鏡班人未必真係講真心說話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T18:06:47.000Z","msg":"英國人"},{"pid":"501022e165e6155c9c3eb658ef108bec6dab27b1","tid":2388471,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f5d9e17077d95de295a14cb171f354232dbff58","tid":2388471,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"上鏡班人未必真係講真心說話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T18:16:41.000Z","msg":"真 等如喺美國唔敢認自己撐侵<br />\n人必自侮而後人侮之<br />\n唔好俾人睇死就得"},{"pid":"6dcf044e0a415ecd891c21505a5a42864662e790","tid":2388471,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T18:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d64a079931b2243f1e2e32d00c410be8eac63a","tid":2388471,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T18:21:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"> 只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 引致百國聯軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>香港獨立戰爭</ins><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>支共無錢發難</ins><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２A：支共無錢發難引致世界大戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>香港獨立戰爭</ins><br />\n<br />\n[軍事小說] 習近平氏の希特拉化！英美德法荷日印澳同盟國形成！普京：依家局勢好似二戰前既30年代！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gCmQrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gCmQrS</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"0ce189564c9dee30321a150790a05b978e385c0c","tid":2388471,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"501022e165e6155c9c3eb658ef108bec6dab27b1","tid":2388471,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f5d9e17077d95de295a14cb171f354232dbff58","tid":2388471,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"上鏡班人未必真係講真心說話"},"citedBy":